\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Every container in Kubernetes has a writable layer called the \tab root filesystem:
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Created automatically when the container starts.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Ephemeral: Data is lost if the container is deleted.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Tied to the container, not the Pod as a whole.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Cannot be shared between containers in the same Pod.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Used for storing temporary data inside the container only.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Key point: This is not defined in the Pod spec, it\hich\f1 \rquote \loch\f1 s the container\hich\f1 \rquote \loch\f1 s internal filesystem.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f1\fs28\cf6\kerning0\insrsid3440241 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 1. emptyDir: \{\}
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs28\kerning0\insrsid3440241 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 emptyDir is a Pod-scoped volume:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f1\fs28\cf6\kerning0\insrsid3440241 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs28\kerning0\insrsid3440241 \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Created\hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1  when a Pod is assigned to a Node.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Data persists as long as the Pod exists.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Deleted when the Pod is deleted.
\par \tab \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Shared between containers in the same Pod.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \ab\af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f1\fs28\cf6\kerning0\insrsid3440241 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Exampleof volume}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs28 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs28\cf1\kerning0\insrsid3440241 \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 :
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 apiVersion: v1
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 kind: Pod
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 metadata:
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1   name: volume-example
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 spec:
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1   containers:
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1   - name: busybox-container
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1     image: busybox
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1     command: ["/bin/sh", "-c", "echo 'Hello from Volume!' > /data/message && sleep 3600"]
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1     volumeMounts:
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1     - name: demo-volume
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1       mountPath: /data
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1   volumes:
