\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1     emptyDir: \{\}
\par --------------------------------------
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 volumeMounts mounts the emptyDir volume into /data.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 Any container in this Pod could also mount /data and share the same data.
\par \hich\af1\dbch\af31505\loch\f1 When the Pod is deleted, the emptyDir and its data are removed automatically.
